# Spotify Music Analysis using Python & Power BI

![Spotify Logo](spotify_logo.png)

## Overview

This project analyzes Spotify music data using Python and Power BI, providing insights into popular artists, energetic tracks, instrumental songs, and much more. The data sources include Kaggle and the Spotify API, ensuring comprehensive coverage.

## Key Findings

### 1. Top 10 Popular Artists

- Drake: 16 songs
- Rick Ross: 13 songs
- Disclosure: 12 songs
- Backstreet Boys: 10 songs
- WALK THE MOON: 10 songs
- FIDLAR: 9 songs
- Crystal Castles: 9 songs
- *NSYNC: 8 songs
- Fall Out Boy: 8 songs
- Michael Jackson: 8 songs

### 2. Loudest Tracks

- GodLovesUgly: -0.307
- The Lion - Original Mix: -0.718
- The Wall: -0.787
- Hey Baby - Steve Aoki Remix: -0.935
- No Absolution: -0.994

### 3. Artists with the Most Danceable Songs

- Ben Remember: Flashwind - Radio Edit (Danceability: 0.984)
- Justin Timberlake: SexyBack (Danceability: 0.967)
- Blaqstarr: Check Me Out Like (Danceability: 0.962)
- Young Thug: Best Friend (Danceability: 0.959)
- Vanilla Ice: Ice Ice Baby (Danceability: 0.959)

### 4. Top 5 Instrumental Songs

- Signs of the Swarm: Senseless Order (Instrumentalness: 0.976)
- Prince Rama: So Destroyed (channeling Rage Peace) (Instrumentalness: 0.968)
- Ray Bryant: A Hundred Dreams from Now (Instrumentalness: 0.964)
- John Dahlbäck: Raven (Instrumentalness: 0.958)
- Todd Terje: Strandbar (disko) (Instrumentalness: 0.957)

### 5. Top 10 Energetic Tracks

- Lyric Pieces, Book I Op. 12: I. Arietta (Energy: 0.0148)
- String Quartet No. 4 in C Major, D. 46: II. Andante con moto (Energy: 0.0156)
- Blue in Green (Energy: 0.0161)
- Piano Quartet in E flat, Op.47: 3. Andante cantabile (Energy: 0.0230)
- 8 Fantasiestücke, Op.12 : 1. Des Abends (Energy: 0.0288)
- Blue and Sentimental (Energy: 0.0291)
- I'm a Fool to Want You (Energy: 0.0295)
- Mozart: Requiem in D Minor, K. 626: VIII. Lacrimosa (Energy: 0.0310)
- Nocturne No.1 In B Flat Minor, Op.9 No.1 (Energy: 0.0347)

### 6. Most Popular Artist

- Drake: 16 songs

### 7. Top 5 Tracks with Most Valence

- Abataka - Original Mix (Valence: 0.992)
- I'm Walkin' - 2002 Digital Remaster (Valence: 0.975)
